      "date": "2013-08-27 22:12:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(4 inline comments)\n\n",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "93a9b600b5ba0f1aad1529e826f84d74f23d2484",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 177,
        "name": "John Hammond",
        "email": "jhammond@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "jhammond"
      },
      "date": "2013-08-27 22:21:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: (3 inline comments)\n\nJC, I do not understand you comment. Could you please elaborate?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "d101e8a4d518f6076938a652871e4bd9150163a2",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 140,
        "name": "jacques-Charles Lafoucriere",
        "email": "jacques-charles.lafoucriere@cea.fr",
        "username": "jcl"
      },
      "date": "2013-08-27 22:27:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe bug is that a user cannot restore a file, only root can do it. So I propose to add new tests to sanity-hsm to validate the patch. Also as we are no more doing the restore as root, we have to be sure we can restore a file in a RO directory.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "a1eb4a853cab912b66b2f28c061676478da484ac",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 177,
        "name": "John Hammond",
        "email": "jhammond@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "jhammond"
      },
      "date": "2013-08-27 22:31:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> The bug is that a user cannot restore a file, only root can do it. So I propose to add new tests to sanity-hsm to validate the patch. Also as we are no more doing the restore as root, we have to be sure we can restore a file in a RO directory.\n\nIndeed. I have validated the patch by hand and am now working on a second patch to restrict the HSM privileges of a non-root user. I planned to add tests for what you mention and for the restrictions in that change.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
